{
  "page": "Walls of Qarth",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Alfred_Khamidullin_Qarth.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/Alfred_Khamidullin_Qarth.jpg/350px-Alfred_Khamidullin_Qarth.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"389\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/Alfred_Khamidullin_Qarth.jpg/525px-Alfred_Khamidullin_Qarth.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ad/Alfred_Khamidullin_Qarth.jpg/700px-Alfred_Khamidullin_Qarth.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Alfred_Khamidullin_Qarth.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a>, by Alfred Khamidullin © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>walls of Qarth</b> are three thick walls that surround <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a>, an ancient port city located on the southern coast of <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. They are among the <a href=\"/index.php/Wonders_Made_by_Man\" title=\"Wonders Made by Man\">wonders of the world</a> according to <a href=\"/index.php/Lomas_Longstrider\" title=\"Lomas Longstrider\">Lomas Longstrider</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Layout\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Layout</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Layout\">Layout</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walls_of_Qarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Layout\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The outer wall, red sandstone thirty feet high, is decorated with carved animals, including <a href=\"/index.php/Snake\" title=\"Snake\">snakes</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Kite\" title=\"Kite\">kites</a>, fish, <a href=\"/index.php/Wolves\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wolves\">wolves</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Zorse\" title=\"Zorse\">zorses</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Elephants\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Elephants\">elephants</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The middle wall, grey granite forty feet high, depicts scenes of war instead of animals.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The innermost wall is made of black <a href=\"/index.php/Marble\" title=\"Marble\">marble</a> fifty feet high and is carved with scenes of lovemaking.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>The city's outer and middle gates are banded with <a href=\"/index.php/Copper\" title=\"Copper\">copper</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Iron\" title=\"Iron\">iron</a>, respectively. The innermost gates are studded with <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">golden</a> eyes.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>    \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walls_of_Qarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>While other <a href=\"/index.php/Qaathi\" title=\"Qaathi\">Qaathi</a> settlements were destroyed by <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Century_of_Blood\" title=\"Century of Blood\">Century of Blood</a>, the triple wall protected <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a> from attack.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walls_of_Qarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walls_of_Qarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:452px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Qarth_Walls_HBO.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/af/Qarth_Walls_HBO.jpg/450px-Qarth_Walls_HBO.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"169\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/af/Qarth_Walls_HBO.jpg/675px-Qarth_Walls_HBO.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/af/Qarth_Walls_HBO.jpg/900px-Qarth_Walls_HBO.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Qarth_Walls_HBO.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The walls of Qarth in <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i></div></div></div>\n<p>All three walls open for <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> when she arrives at <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_waste\" title=\"Red waste\">red waste</a>. Men beat gongs from atop the walls to herald her coming.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walls_of_Qarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>As <a href=\"/index.php/Yezzan_zo_Qaggaz\" title=\"Yezzan zo Qaggaz\">Yezzan zo Qaggaz</a> lies dying during the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_siege_of_Meereen\" title=\"Second siege of Meereen\">second siege of Meereen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a> suggests sailing to Qarth and tells <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> of the city walls. However, Tyrion informs her that he has no intention of going any further east.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walls_of_Qarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>In the south, other <a href=\"/index.php/Khal\" title=\"Khal\">khals</a> led their hordes into the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Waste\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Red Waste\">Red Waste</a>, destroying the <a href=\"/index.php/Qaathi\" title=\"Qaathi\">Qaathi</a> towns and cities that once dotted that desert, until only the great city of <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a> remained, protected by its towering triple wall.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;writings of <a href=\"/index.php/Yandel\" title=\"Yandel\">Yandel</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Three thick walls encircled <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a>, elaborately carved. The outer was red sandstone, thirty feet high and decorated with animals: <a href=\"/index.php/Snake\" title=\"Snake\">snakes</a> slithering, <a href=\"/index.php/Kite\" title=\"Kite\">kites</a> flying, fish swimming, intermingled with <a href=\"/index.php/Wolves\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wolves\">wolves</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_waste\" title=\"Red waste\">red waste</a> and striped <a href=\"/index.php/Zorse\" title=\"Zorse\">zorses</a> and monstrous <a href=\"/index.php/Elephant\" title=\"Elephant\">elephants</a>. The middle wall, forty feet high, was grey granite alive with scenes of war: the clash of sword and shield and spear, arrows in flight, heroes at battle and babes being butchered, pyres of the dead. The innermost wall was fifty feet of black <a href=\"/index.php/Marble\" title=\"Marble\">marble</a>, with carvings that made Dany blush until she told herself that she was being a <a href=\"/index.php/Fool\" title=\"Fool\">fool</a>. She was no <a href=\"/index.php/Maid\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maid\">maid</a>; if she could look on the grey wall's scenes of slaughter, why should she avert her eyes from the sight of men and women giving pleasure to one another?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Penny</b>: We could sail to <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a>. The streets are paved with <a href=\"/index.php/Jade\" title=\"Jade\">jade</a> there, <a href=\"/index.php/Oppo\" title=\"Oppo\">my brother</a> always said. The city walls are one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Wonders_Made_by_Man\" title=\"Wonders Made by Man\">wonders of the world</a>. When we perform in Qarth, <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Silver\" title=\"Silver\">silver</a> will rain down on us, you'll see.<br />\n<b>Tyrion</b>: Some of those ships out on <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">the bay</a> are Qartheen. <a href=\"/index.php/Lomas_Longstrider\" title=\"Lomas Longstrider\">Lomas Longstrider</a> saw the walls of Qarth. His books suffice for me. I have gone as far east as I intend to go.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walls_of_Qarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_57\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 57\">Chapter 57</a>, Tyrion XI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\">2.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\">2.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Daenerys II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: The Grasslands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403132434\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.038 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.040 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1183/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9054/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6096/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2399/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3892/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   24.999      1 -total\n 81.49%   20.372     11 Template:Ref\n 52.26%   13.065     11 Template:Ref/core\n 24.13%    6.032      3 Template:Quote\n 11.22%    2.806      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:19524-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403132434 and revision id 333318\n -->\n",
